{"tid":1174430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本川崎市發生隨機持刀傷人　至少16人遭刺傷　包括8名兒童","createTime":"2019-05-28T00:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T10:19:00.000Z","uid":237397,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2db2e6ec8a2a4de92e093cd362bdc4bea52a4e20","tid":1174430,"uid":237397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T00:11:19.000Z","msg":"日本共同社及日本放送協會（NHK）等媒體報道，當地周二（28日）上午7時45分發生持刀傷人血案，據稱傷者都是被隨機刺傷，至少16人受傷，當中包括8名兒童。警方到場拘捕一名持刀男子，正調查他犯案動機，及捜索是否有同黨。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方指出，事發地點距離小田急線登戸站約200米的公園附近，懷疑一名男子用刀刺傷途人。當地媒體引述消防部門報道，事件造成至少16人受傷，當中一名兒童及兩名成人心肺停止。<br />\n<br />\nNHK引述當地街坊指出，事發地點經常有孩子遊玩。有報道指疑犯被捕前曾自殘，刺傷自己肩膀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/333837/日本川崎市發生隨機持刀傷人-至少16人遭刺傷-包括8名兒童\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F333837%2F%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%B7%9D%E5%B4%8E%E5%B8%82%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E9%9A%A8%E6%A9%9F%E6%8C%81%E5%88%80%E5%82%B7%E4%BA%BA-%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9116%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E5%88%BA%E5%82%B7-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC8%E5%90%8D%E5%85%92%E7%AB%A5&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQXXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=54b6080c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/333837/日本川崎市發生隨機持刀傷人-至少16人遭刺傷-包括8名兒童</a><br />\n暫時得hk01有報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起當年秋葉原無差別殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇日本新聞依家共19人受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 3人心肺停止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c29bf13bcf62bc18cb3369bb62ff96e5d5e86b","tid":1174430,"uid":254461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T00:49:59.000Z","msg":"犯人40至59歲"},{"pid":"671c0ed9f45d8510f2b1f891172489f27d632a3b","tid":1174430,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci